\begin_inset Formula $100,100,10,10$
\end_inset

 and the constant 
\begin_inset Formula $c_{1,}c_{2}$
\end_inset

 to 
\begin_inset Formula $1,$
\end_inset

the resulting matrix would be:
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\Gamma^{'}=\mbox{\ensuremath{\left[\begin{array}{rrrr}
